  "original_title": "\u0b8f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0baa\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Why not replace the patriot",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A letter has been sent by the Attorney General to the Attorney General regarding the dismissal of the Attorney General's request for the immediate transfer of Deshabandhu Tennakoon, the Senior Deputy Inspector General of Police in charge of the Upper Province.",
        "The letter said that the non-relocation of Patriot Tennakoon would put pressure on police investigations into the May 9 riots.",
        "The letter also noted that the court had recently instructed the Attorney General to state the reason for not advancing the transfer."
      ],
